  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Duffryn Nurture Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This proposal seeks to provide revenue funding to support a short fall in on -going revenue costs for the &#x2018;nurture&apos; project that operates in the Infant and Junior schools in Duffryn, Newport. The project has delivered direct and clear outcomes on education, inter -personal behaviour and emotion management for over 220 children over the past 10 years, as well as providing an access point for intervention with 24 families. The built up knowledge and track record of this amazing programme risks being lost, as well as the immediate removal of benefits for current participants.</narrative>
  </description>
